{"id":130,"date":"2018-12-17T03:49:08","date_gmt":"2018-12-17T03:49:08","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/khachsan1.khowebseotop.vn\/?p=130"},"modified":"2021-05-13T10:41:20","modified_gmt":"2021-05-13T03:41:20","slug":"duong-vao-dam-sen-hoa-no-bat-ngan-o-nha-trang","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/khachsan1.webtudong8giay.com\/duong-vao-dam-sen-hoa-no-bat-ngan-o-nha-trang\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7m sen hoa n\u1edf b\u1ea1t ng\u00e0n \u1edf Nha Trang"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>T\u00f4i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tr\u00e0m Chim, Ph\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ed3ng,\u00a0<strong>Nha Trang<\/strong>. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i theo \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5t Th\u00e0nh v\u00e0o trung t\u00e2m x\u00e3 Ph\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ed3ng, ngay ng\u00e3 ba \u0111i s\u00e2n bay Cam Ranh, r\u1ebd v\u1ec1 h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u1ea3i, \u0111i ch\u1eebng h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t km th\u1ea5y t\u1ea5m b\u1ea3ng b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ecf: \u201c\u0110\u1ea3m tr\u00e0m chim\u201d.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_250201\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\">\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-250201 size-full\" title=\"Khu \u0111\u1ea7m c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i \u0111i b\u1eb1ng tre \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch tham quan.\" src=\"http:\/\/khachsan1.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/duong-vao-dam-sen-hoa-no-bat-ngan-o-nha-trang-130.jpg\" alt=\"Khu \u0111\u1ea7m c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i \u0111i b\u1eb1ng tre \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch tham quan.\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Khu \u0111\u1ea7m c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i \u0111i b\u1eb1ng tre \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch tham quan.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>Ph\u00f3ng xe \u0111i ti\u1ebfp qua khu d\u00e2n c\u01b0, l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ru\u1ed9ng, bao quanh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1eeda ru\u1ed9ng tr\u1ed3ng rau mu\u1ed1ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian y\u00ean \u1eafng v\u00e0 thanh b\u00ecnh. R\u1ed3i t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc l\u1ec1u l\u1ee3p l\u00e1, c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea7m sen b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1edf hoa. Ngay t\u1ee9c kh\u1eafc, t\u00f4i b\u1ecb v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y m\u00ea ho\u1eb7c.<\/p>\n<p>N\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n hoang s\u01a1 v\u00e0 b\u00ecnh d\u1ecb. Nh\u1eefng \u1ee5 r\u01a1m ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m duy\u00ean, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3nh m\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu tr\u1eef l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ef1c cho gia s\u00fac. M\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea5t bao quanh \u0111\u1ea7m sen r\u1ed9ng 2.000 m\u00e9t vu\u00f4ng n\u00e0y. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2m s\u1eaft cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e2y b\u1ea7u, c\u00e2y m\u01b0\u1edbp leo l\u00ean. C\u00f4 b\u00e9 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean h\u1ed3n nhi\u00ean b\u1ea3o kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 tham quan, ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_250203\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\">\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-250203 size-full\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, \u0103n u\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u00f3n d\u00e2n d\u00e3.\" src=\"http:\/\/khachsan1.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/duong-vao-dam-sen-hoa-no-bat-ngan-o-nha-trang-130-1.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, \u0103n u\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u00f3n d\u00e2n d\u00e3.\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, \u0103n u\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u00f3n d\u00e2n d\u00e3.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>\u0110\u1ea7m sen Ph\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ed3ng,\u00a0<strong><em>Nha Trang<\/em><\/strong>\u00a0nguy\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t tr\u0169ng, x\u01b0a tr\u1ed3ng rau mu\u1ed1ng. T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2017, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 anh \u0110\u1ea3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n qua tr\u1ed3ng hoa sen. Gi\u1ed1ng hoa anh ch\u1ecdn tr\u1ed3ng l\u1ea5y t\u1eeb \u0110\u1ed3ng Th\u00e1p, l\u00e1 v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7, hoa nh\u1ecf ph\u1edbt h\u1ed3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2017 c\u01a1n b\u00e3o s\u1ed1 12 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y thi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea7m sen. Gi\u1edd anh g\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc l\u1ec1u, sen b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1edf trong \u0111\u1ea7m m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc c\u1ea7u tre \u0111an xen trong \u0111\u1ea7m, c\u00f3 khi hoa sen c\u00f9ng m\u1ecdc ngay tr\u00ean c\u1ea7u. Kh\u00e1ch \u0111i theo nh\u1eefng nh\u00e1nh r\u1ebd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 ng\u1eafm nh\u00ecn, t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng. Kh\u00e1ch \u0111i m\u1ecfi ch\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 chi\u1ebfc l\u1ec1u n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Kh\u00f4ng gian bao quanh n\u01a1i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t im \u1eafng, kh\u00f4ng \u1ed3n \u00e0o ti\u1ebfng xe c\u1ed9; xa xa l\u00e0 n\u00fai, c\u00e1nh r\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1edbc nguy\u00ean sinh, ru\u1ed9ng \u0111ang non t\u01a1 m\u00e0u xanh l\u00faa m\u1edbi. Khi chi\u1ec1u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, n\u1eafng nghi\u00eang sau n\u00fai, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e0n chim bay v\u1ec1 r\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1edbc, qua \u0111\u1ea7m sen, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3nh s\u1eafc tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_250202\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\">\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-250202 size-full\" title=\"Khu \u0111\u1ea7m n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb trung t\u00e2m ra s\u00e2n bay Cam Ranh.\" src=\"http:\/\/khachsan1.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/duong-vao-dam-sen-hoa-no-bat-ngan-o-nha-trang-130-2.jpg\" alt=\"Khu \u0111\u1ea7m n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb trung t\u00e2m ra s\u00e2n bay Cam Ranh.\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Khu \u0111\u1ea7m n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb trung t\u00e2m ra s\u00e2n bay Cam Ranh.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u00f4i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tr\u00e0m Chim, Ph\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ed3ng,\u00a0Nha Trang. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i theo \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5t Th\u00e0nh v\u00e0o trung t\u00e2m x\u00e3 Ph\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ed3ng, ngay ng\u00e3 ba \u0111i s\u00e2n bay Cam Ranh, r\u1ebd v\u1ec1 h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u1ea3i, \u0111i ch\u1eebng h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t km th\u1ea5y t\u1ea5m b\u1ea3ng b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":133,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[17],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/khachsan1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/130"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/khachsan1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/khachsan1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/khachsan1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/khachsan1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=130"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/khachsan1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/130\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":135,"href":"https:\/\/khachsan1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/130\/revisions\/135"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/khachsan1.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/133"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/khachsan1.webtu